{"tid":1743635,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"何謂愛國？","createTime":"2019-11-21T09:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T09:58:51.000Z","uid":184010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea48e46c3849f67c35e0295f3f420f20f90b449e","tid":1743635,"uid":184010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"民權興則國權立，民權滅則國權亡。為君相者而務壓民之權，是之謂自棄其國；為民者而不務各伸其權，是之謂自棄其身。故言愛國必自興民權始<br />\n<br />\n- - 《愛國論》<br />\n<br />\n麻煩send比d藍絲睇"},{"pid":"2716d9c6dfd2e35940508f0f0b0bbb061612ec44","tid":1743635,"uid":184010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">故言愛國必自興民權始</span></span><br />\n即係話你們柒頭連民權都無 無資格愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9c6b8b3ac6ce210757cd5ab9b04382062e4f11","tid":1743635,"uid":312242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"睇下愛邊個國家啦<br />\n<br />\n如果你愛嘅係冇一個国家 咁你就要送曬你啲仔女去外國讀書 去平民百姓度掠水 去做豆腐渣工程 去買架意大利法拉利林寶堅尼 仲要掛嗰個咁核突嘅国旗喺上面"}]}